author: Screen Junkies
description:
Mr Beast discusses everything from YouTuber tax-evasion strategies to making Jurassic Park for real. We dive deep into the Beast Games, A/B testing breakfast, and the secret burner accounts he uses to argue with 12-year-olds. Watch until the end to see if we successfully bribe him to delete his channel for forty bucks and some teriyaki sticks.

Voice Narration: Jon Bailey the EPIC VOICE GUY (@epicvoiceguy on all socials)

#honesttrailers #mrbeast #beastgames
title: MrBeast: The Honest Interview
